<L>__{exterior broken catwalk day}
<A>__{paul, grant and amanda struggle to stay away from the pteranodon as it moves towards them. suddenly. the far end of this inverted section of catwalk detaches from the canyon wall and}
<B>__{swings downward.}
<A>__{the force of the action sends the three tumbling directly towards the pteranodon. miraculously, they manage to avoid its open beak. but they are all sent plummeting toward the river below.}
<L>__{exterior river day}
<A>__{they hit the water hard, resurfacing moments later. the current is carrying them downstream.}
